HEADWORD: barrel cactus
<hw>bar"rel cac"tus</hw> <pr>(b⟦acr⟧r"r⟦ecr⟧l k⟦acr⟧k"t⟦ucr⟧s)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos>; <plu>pl. <plw>barrel cacti</plw> <pr>(b⟦acr⟧r"r⟦ecr⟧l
